"3763-12140602R" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The power supplies shown in the FCC photos are... *a '''Hon-Kwang''' HK-J106-A12 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz, 0.2A -> 12VDC, 0-0.5A) *an ''unbranded'' 3A-061WP12 (100-240VAC ~ 50-60Hz, 0.3A -> 12VDC, 0.5A)
Default settings are per the FCC manual and may (very likely) be inaccurate..
